structure of parameter file
d                dimension of the system
Nt               t lattice extension
Nx               x lattice extension
Ny               y lattice extension
Nz               z lattice extension
d_field          dimension of the field(n of components)
N_meas           number of measurements
N_term           number of thermalization steps
N_sweeps         number of sweep steps
mass             mass parameter(free theory coupling)
lambda           lambda parameter(phi^4 coupling)
g                g parameter(phi^6 coupling)
kappa            kappa parameter(phi^3 coupling)
delta            control parameter for Metropolis
dt               flow time integration interval
N_steps          number of integration steps